E7%A8%B1%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7-%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E6%95%99%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A7.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.gospelherald.com%2Farticles%2F29251%2F20201023%2F%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%259D%25A3%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25AD%25A7.htm&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=c90a6544\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.gospelherald.com/articles/29251/20201023/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E7%A8%B1%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7-%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E6%95%99%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%8F%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A7.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n拜登稱支持兒童變性 基督教回應現大分歧<br />\n<br />\n美國總統競選進行如火如荼，<span class=\"red\">民主黨總統候選人拜登在市民大會發言指，8歲兒童可變性</span>。福音派人士對此看法分成兩極，反對者斥拜登撒謊、支持者指提醒大眾對變性的認識。<br />\n<br />\n拜登支持跨性別達零歧視<br />\n<br />\n拜登（Joe Biden）在10月15日出席美國廣播公司新聞市民大會回應觀眾對變性的看法，直言支持跨性別及零歧視。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，<span class=\"red\">不應剝奪跨性別孩子進行變性的權利，孩子到8歲至10歲已經有獨立的思考</span>，有自我識別的能力做出改變人生及性別的決定，任何人包括父母在內也不能否認孩子的權利。<br />\n<br />\n近年LGBT 激進團體在學校推動設立跨性別設施，例如浴室及洗手間，不論任何性別的人皆可進入。<br />\n<br />\n反對者斥謊言 支持者指非激進<br />\n<br />\n拜登的言論引起社會人士的討論，有神學教授、牧師紛紛在推特貼文各持正反意見。<br />\n<br />\n美南浸信會神學院博伊斯學院（Boyce College）教授丹尼&middot;伯克（Denny Burk）在推特發文駁斥拜登言論，是向未成年兒童宣傳謊言歪曲事實。<br />\n<br />\n德克薩斯州普萊諾市伍德浸信會（Prestonwood Baptist Church in Plano） 傑克&middot;格雷厄姆牧師（Rev. Jack Graham）感到震驚，<span class=\"red\">表示以耶穌之名不可能投票給這種疑似虐待狂、變態的人</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不過，美南浸信會神學院倫理系及神學教授安德魯&middot;沃克（Andrew Walker）卻持相反意見，認為共和黨總統川普的政策不可信而支持拜登，指出有拜登的追隨者屬於福音派信徒，他們的道德標準在社會作公開見證或許會制衡拜登不致偏離信仰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T13:44:26.000Z","msg":"支持佢又點制衡佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb796ed85ed2917df6e6a99904d18c18e500c509","tid":2256132,"uid":232295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T14:00:34.000Z","msg":"拜登講乜都得架啦<br />\n反正佢得一個政綱anyone but trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9468e7ec8619d36300db56435cc9eadbb99bed97","tid":2256132,"uid":336948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"發育都未定就變性 係咪冇腦 投左膠所好投到一啲腦都冇 離地到仆街"},{"pid":"043cf4808c7ac64cd5b083a3d9412b545fa849e8","tid":2256132,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb796ed85ed2917df6e6a99904d18c18e500c509","tid":2256132,"uid":232295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T14:00:34.000Z","msg":"拜登講乜都得架啦<br />\n反正佢得一個政綱anyone but trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"佢辯論好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人本身已經老<br />\n講得出嘅政策同願景寥寥可數之餘<br />\n仲要好唔具體 好抽象<br />\n純屬只係因反侵而生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11a1a2e515a46e8854adf046f27d96157d0d557","tid":2256132,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T14:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2e2298d4fa131f4c69dcf67852d680e85b6307","tid":2256132,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"跟住係咪支持亂輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06d57d2982221b71caf53862d8e354c4b9265d1","tid":2256132,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dbb7acce592a7a9a84c81da396a6ebc58c6c11","tid":2256132,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s